  inherit eutils for epatch

  16 Mar 2004; <augustus@gentoo.org> arson-0.9.7-r3.ebuild:
  Marked ~amd64.

  14 Mar 2004; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> arson-0.9.7-r3.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc.

  14 Mar 2004; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> arson-0.9.7-r3.ebuild:
  inherit kde instead of deprecated kde-base

  27 Dec 2003; Caleb Tennis <caleb@gentoo.org> arson-0.9.7-r1.ebuild,
  arson-0.9.7-r2.ebuild, arson-0.9.7-r3.ebuild, arson-0.9.7.ebuild:
  remove old versions - fix dependency stuff

  05 Dec 2003; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> arson-0.9.7.ebuild:
  Changed sparc keyword to ~sparc as numerous dependencies were masked. Need
  further time to test.

